full_text: The year is 2040. @HeyCam93 has a new co-host on Chatting Average because @RileysRakes has succumbed to age and, frankly, @JeffMDonahoo ain’t getting any younger either. In “this day in baseball history” Cam fondly reflects on a 3-16 Braves win on Austin Riley bobblehead night.
